            <title><![CDATA[Famitsu Sales: 3/30/26 – 4/5/26]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/04/famitsu-sales-3-30-26-4-5-26</link>
            <guid>1486342</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Pokemon Pokopia remains the top seller.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a href="https://www.famitsu.com/article/202604/71349" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Famitsu</a> has published its estimated physical game software data for Japan for the week of March 30, 2026 to April 5, 2026. <span id="more-1039448"></span></p><p><em><a title="Games > Pokemon Pokopia [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-pokopia">Pokemon Pokopia</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> 2 remained the highest selling game of the week, moving an additional 45,484 retail copies.</p><p>On the hardware side, Switch 2 sold 59,543 units, the Switch family sold 16,342 units, the <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> family sold 13,539 units, and the <a title="Platforms > Xbox [27,577 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox">Xbox</a> Series family sold 932 units.</p><p>Get the full sales charts below.</p><p><strong>Software Sales</strong> (followed by lifetime sales)</p><ol><li>[SW2]&nbsp;<em>Pokemon Pokopia</em> (<a title="Companies > The Pokemon Company [444 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/the-pokemon-company">The Pokemon Company</a>, 03/05/26) – 45,484 (867,171)</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Mario Kart World [18 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mario-kart-world">Mario Kart World</a></em> (<a title="Platforms > Nintendo [23,696 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a>, 06/05/25) – 8,131 (2,888,474)</li><li>[NSW] <em>Minecraft</em> (Microsoft, 06/21/18) – 5,186 (4,182,507)</li><li>[NSW]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Mega Man Star Force Legacy Collection [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mega-man-star-force-legacy-collection">Mega Man Star Force Legacy Collection</a></em> (<a title="Companies > Capcom [2,662 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a>, 03/27/26) – 4,956 (23,194)</li><li>[NSW] <em>Animal Crossing: New Horizons</em> (Nintendo, 03/20/20) – 4,710 (8,415,833)</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/monster-hunter-stories-3-twisted-reflection">Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection</a></em> (Capcom, 03/13/26) – 4,588 (58,077)</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Super Mario Bros. Wonder - Nintendo Switch 2 Edition + Meetup in Bellabel Park [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/super-mario-bros-wonder-nintendo-switch-2-edition-meetup-in-bellabel-park">Super Mario Bros. Wonder – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition + Meetup in Bellabel Park</a></em> (Nintendo, 03/26/26) – 4,324 (14,482)</li><li>[NSW]&nbsp;<em><a title="Series > Pokemon [44 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/pokemon">Pokemon</a> FireRed Version</em> /&nbsp;<em>LeafGreen Version</em> (Download Card) (The Pokemon Company, 02/28/26) – 4,146 (15,292)</li><li>[PS5]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Crimson Desert [27 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/crimson-desert">Crimson Desert</a></em> (<a title="Companies > Pearl Abyss [43 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/pearl-abyss">Pearl Abyss</a>, 03/19/26) – 3,812 (40,185)</li><li>[SW2]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Animal Crossing: New Horizons [41 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/animal-crossing-new-horizons">Animal Crossing: New Horizons – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition</a></em> (Nintendo, 01/15/26) – 3,706 (98,786)</li></ol><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Rankings 11 to 30 will be announced on April 10.</p><ol><li>[NSW] <em><a title="Games > Winning Post 10 2026 [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/winning-post-10-2026">Winning Post 10 2026</a></em> (<a title="Companies > Koei Tecmo Games [3,129 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games">Koei Tecmo</a>, 03/26/26) –</li><li>[SW2]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Mario Tennis Fever [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mario-tennis-fever">Mario Tennis Fever</a></em> (Nintendo, 02/12/26) –</li><li>[PS5]&nbsp;<em>Winning Post 10 2026</em> (Koei Tecmo, 03/26/26) –</li><li>[SW2] <em>Winning Post 10 2026</em> (Koei Tecmo, 03/26/26) –</li><li>[PS5]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Resident Evil Requiem [19 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/resident-evil-requiem">Resident Evil Requiem</a></em> (Capcom, 02/27/26) –</li><li>[NSW]&nbsp;<em>Handsome Laundering: the mystic lover</em> (<a title="Companies > Edia [46 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/edia">Edia</a>, 03/26/26) –</li><li>[NSW]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Okayu Nyumu! R [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/okayu-nyumu-r">Okayu Nyumu! R</a></em> (<a title="Companies > Entergram [209 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/entergram">Entergram</a>, 03/26/26) –</li><li>[NSW] <em><a title="Games > Pokemon Legends: Z-A [19 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-legends-z-a">Pokemon Legends: Z-A</a></em> (The Pokemon Company, 10/16/25) –</li><li>[NSW] <em><a title="Games > Super Smash Bros. Ultimate [68 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/super-smash-bros-ultimate">Super Smash Bros. Ultimate</a></em> (Nintendo, 12/07/18) –</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Pokemon Legends: Z-A - Nintendo Switch 2 Edition [16 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-legends-z-a-nintendo-switch-2-edition">Pokemon Legends: Z-A – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition</a></em> (The Pokemon Company, 10/16/25) –</li><li>[PS5] <em>Mega Man Star Force Legacy Collection</em> (Capcom, 03/27/26) –</li><li>[NSW] <em>Mario Kart 8 Deluxe</em> (Nintendo, 04/28/17) –</li><li>[NSW]&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > TAITO Milestones 4 [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/taito-milestones-4">TAITO Milestones 4</a></em> (<a title="Companies > TAITO [151 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/taito">TAITO</a>, 03/26/26) –</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Momotaro Dentetsu 2: Anata no Machi mo Kitto Aru - Higashi Nihon Hen + Nishi Nihon Hen [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/momotaro-dentetsu-2-anata-no-machi-mo-kitto-aru-higashi-nihon-hen-nishi-nihon-hen">Momotaro Dentetsu 2: Anata no Machi mo Kitto Aru – Higashi Nihon Hen + Nishi Nihon Hen</a> – <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Nintendo Switch 2</a> Edition</em> (<a title="Companies > Konami Digital Entertainment [1,169 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/konami">Konami</a>, 11/13/25) –</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Super Mario Party Jamboree - Nintendo Switch 2 Edition + Jamboree TV [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/super-mario-party-jamboree-nintendo-switch-2-edition-jamboree-tv">Super Mario Party Jamboree – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition + Jamboree TV</a></em> (Nintendo, 07/24/25) –</li><li>[NSW] <em><a title="Games > Dragon Quest VII Reimagined [18 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined">Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</a></em> (<a title="Companies > Square Enix [5,440 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/square-enix">Square Enix</a>, 02/05/26) –</li><li>[SW2] <em><a title="Games > Kirby Air Riders [11 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/kirby-air-riders">Kirby Air Riders</a></em> (Nintendo, 11/20/25) –</li><li>[NSW] <em>Momotaro Dentetsu 2: Anata no Machi mo Kitto Aru – Higashi Nihon Hen + Nishi Nihon Hen</em> (Konami, 11/13/25) –</li><li>[NSW] <em><a title="Games > Super Mario Party Jamboree [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/super-mario-party-jamboree">Super Mario Party Jamboree</a></em> (Nintendo, 10/17/24) –</li><li>[SW2] <em>Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</em> (Square Enix, 02/05/26) –</li></ol><p><strong>Hardware Sales</strong> (followed by lifetime sales)</p><ol><li>Switch 2 – 59,543 (5,011,059)</li><li>PlayStation 5 Digital Edition – 12,141 (1,248,515)</li><li>Switch OLED Model – 7,468 (9,526,329)</li><li>Switch Lite – 4,807 (6,903,964)</li><li>Switch – 4,067 (20,0271,045)</li><li>PlayStation 5 Pro – 840 (341,548)</li><li>PlayStation 5 – 558 (5,910,474)</li><li><a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series X</a> – 525 (325,952)</li><li>Xbox Series X Digital Edition – 278 (29,362)</li><li>Xbox Series S – 129 (341,622)</li></ol></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/04/famitsu-sales-3-30-26-4-5-26]]></content:encoded>
